<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Order of the Ministry of National Defense (89) No. 8900006241 of the Republic of China on May 6, 2000.The full text of the 15 articles will be published; and will be implemented as of the date of publication.
2.Amendment to Decree No. 0930000441 of the Ministry of National Defense of the Republic of China on April 28, 2004. Issue Articles 5, 6, 8, and 10
3.Amendment to the Ministry of National Defense, No. 0950000854, Order of the Republic of China on September 28, 2006. The full text of the 15 articles was issued; and it was implemented on September 1, 2006.
4.Amendment of the Order No. 0970000015 of the National Committee of the Ministry of National Defense of the Republic of China on January 4, 2008. Issue Articles 5 and 15; and implement from the release date.
5.Order No. 1030000213 of the National Regulations Committee of the Ministry of National Defense of the Republic of China on August 18, 2014. Amend the provisions of clauses 5, 6, 8, 11, and 15; delete the provisions of Article 10; Daily execution.
6.Order No. 1080000222 of the National Regulations Committee of the Ministry of National Defense of the Republic of China on August 2, 2019. Articles 5, 6, 8, 9, 12 to 14 are being issued.
